<import src="../../template/template.wxml" />
<template is="footer" data="{{activeType}}" />
<view class='pubCover' hidden='{{pubCoverHide}}'></view>

<view class='alertBox1' hidden='{{alertBoxOneHide}}'>
  <view class='title'>恭喜您抽中iphoneX一台</view>
  <image class='alerBox1Img' src="../../images/other/title.png"></image>
  <view class='upBox'>
    <view class='up'>暂不领取</view>
    <view class='postGuess'>立即领取</view>
  </view>
</view>
<view class='alertBox2' hidden='{{alertBoxTwoHide}}'>
    <view class='title'>恭喜您抽中iphoneX一台</view>
     <view class='goodsBox'>
      <image class='goodsImg' src='../../images/other/title.png'></image>
      <view class="goodsName">ipone8</view>
      <view class="goodstype">128g 银色</view>
      <view class='bottom'>
        <view class='username' bindtap='checkAddress'>收件人：六月的风</view>
        <view class='address' bindtap='checkAddress'>地址：福建省福州市</view>
        <view class='upBox'>
          <view class='up' bindtap='closePage'>修改</view>
          <view class='postGuess'>确认</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
</view>
<image src="../../images/other/titlebg.jpg" class='titleBg'></image>
<view class='activeBox'>
  <image src="../../images/other/title.png" class='titleImg'></image>
  <view class='drawBox'>
    <image src="../../images/other/drawbg1.png" class='drawbg'></image>
    <view class="rotate">
      <image animation="{{animationData}}" class="rotate_disk" src="../../images/other/drawbg.png"></image>
      <image class="rotate_btn" bindtap='goDraw' src="../../images/other/get.png"></image>
      <image class="rotate_btnc" src="../../images/other/3.png"></image>
    </view>
    <image src="../../images/other/shadow.png" class='shadow'></image>
  </view>
  <view class='countNum'>
    <text>剩余抽奖次数:6次  剩余积分:15分</text>
  </view>
  <view class='activeRuleBox'>
    <image src='../../images/other/rule.png' class='ruleImg'></image>
    <image src='../../images/other/zq.png' class='zq'></image>
    <view>1.抽奖一次会消耗一积分，积分记入总分</view>
    <view>2.抽奖次数将会累计，抽奖开始时间
      <text>6月14号9点开始到7月16号18点</text> 单次积分抽奖结束</view>
    <view>3.凡显示有抽奖机会的用户都可参与抽奖，不显示则需要参与首页竞猜活动获得机会</view>
    <view>4.总共5个奖品，每个奖品的中奖概率相同</view>
    <view>5.中奖信息在首页显示 </view>
    <view>6.抽奖获得的奖品会在我的显示，提交地址后会在1~3个工作日发货，节假日不发货。 </view>
    <view>7.活动过程中如发现违规作弊行为，我公司有权取消您已获得的奖品，必要时追究法律责任 </view>
  </view>
  <image src='../../images/other/bottombg.jpg' class='bottombg'></image>
  <view class='botomBlock'></view>
</view>